<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>冬天来了。花儿都枯死了，风刮得非常冷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘一直穿着一件叶子做的衣服，最后连那件衣服也破了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她没有办法给自己保暖，也没有食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都去哪里了？”拇指姑娘大声问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“除了我之外每个人都有一个家吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上，拇指姑娘在一片干燥的玉米地里醒来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大片的雪花落在她的周围。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要找一个安全的地方。”她看着四周说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，拇指姑娘看到玉米壳旁有一个黑黑的洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个洞看起来是个睡觉的好地方。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要在里面躲一会儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘走到那个洞边，往里看了一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么，这里有一扇门！”她大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她敲了敲门，门开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的天哪！”一只老鼠大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看起来快要被冻僵了。快进来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘感激地往前走了一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等一下！先擦一下你的脚。”老鼠指着地上的一块垫子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘终于进入了房间。房间又温暖又舒服，还很干净。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是拇指姑娘。”她说，“你的家真好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道，我是格雷夫人。在这里等一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我给你拿一些吃的东西来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘坐在椅子上，马上睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她醒来的时候，格雷夫人给了她一些吃的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘又睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘很虚弱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可怜的小东西。”格雷夫人说，“我会好好照顾你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她照顾着拇指姑娘。很快拇指姑娘恢复了许多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要怎么感谢你呢？”有一天，拇指姑娘问格雷夫人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格雷夫人正在擦家具。她想了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我老了。”她最后说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你想留下来，你就要帮助我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从那天开始，格雷夫人教会了拇指姑娘很多事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要那样拿着针。”格雷夫人边教拇指姑娘缝纫边说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“白萝卜不要煮太长时间。”格雷夫人教拇指姑娘怎样做饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘学得很快。格雷夫人说的事情，她都做了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，格雷夫人看着拇指姑娘缝东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘她就是按照我教给她的方法在做。’格雷夫人骄傲地对自己说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时拇指姑娘第一次唱起了歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘她的声音真美妙！’格雷夫人心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她突然有了一个主意。那是一个好主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘是的，拇指姑娘会很合适的。’她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘她会成为洛夫斯先生完美的新娘。’</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>